prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D comic book style illustration for a greeting card cover. In an explosive and dynamic comic book panel, Jordan and Lao Lao from the photo are transformed into vibrant superheroes. The scene is a split-panel composition with a jagged, electrifying line separating two colorful backgrounds. On the left side, behind Jordan, is a bright yellow background with red Ben-Day dots. On the right side, behind Lao Lao, is a vibrant cyan background with dark blue speed lines radiating outwards.

Jordan, wearing his maroon t-shirt, strikes a confident hero pose, winking and giving a thumbs-up to the viewer. He's surrounded by crackling energy effects. Lao Lao, in her yellow floral top and glasses, has a joyful, energetic expression, one hand raised in a peace sign while the other playfully launches a shower of confetti and glitter that drifts across the entire scene. Their illustrated forms are defined by bold black outlines and flat, saturated colors.

In the center of the card, layered over the jagged split line, is a large, classic comic book sound effect bubble, like "KAPOW!" or "ZAP!". Inside this bubble, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan!". Scattered around the main characters are smaller, fun comic book action words like "BOOM!" and "WOW!".
